body_html: Hi, try to import _pywrap_tensorflow.so in [PYTHON_INSTALL_DIR]/site-packages/tensorflow/python/_pywrap_tensorflow.so this most of the time provides more specific on why it is not loading. Most of the time this happens is because its not able to link to a dynamic library somewhere in your environment, or a minor version changed from a dynamic lib. After that you can take it from there.
